{
  "stem": "812.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And in fact, a cousin of ours was-- was among those that-- but nevertheless, the fact that we were allowed to go to Bergen-Belsen rather than Auschwitz, because we were in that group to be exchanged, saved our lives.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we're forever grateful to my aunt, who made those arrangements in Palestine.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She's-- it's now Israel, and I just saw her a few weeks ago, and she's doing just fine.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I cannot recall the complete incident, but I do know that it happened.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember it vividly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In fact, when I speak to my brother Al about it, he doesn't even remember it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He does not remember it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there-- mind-- a mind does play tricks on-- on-- on-- on people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We-- there's certain things that I recall vividly that my mother doesn't remember.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And as you have seen earlier, my mother remembers things, and-- and by right, she-- she should, being that she was older and so.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But it-- it's-- it was just very comforting to know that a young man like that was not so completely influenced and taken in by the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it-- it-- again, it helped us along in a very, very difficult time-- actually, the-- the-- the worst of times.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I just remember that it was springtime when we arrived in Trobitz.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And although I was preoccupied with the welfare of my burned leg and-- it was very pretty.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a farm village, and with old cobblestone streets and farmhouses, quaint farmhouses, and pretty greenery, grass, trees in bloom, flowers.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it must have been a beautiful time, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] but just I don't think I gave myself the chance to really enjoy it as much.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
